{
  "text": "Deep learning has been the most noticeable direction of machine learning during recent years. Since A fast learning algorithm for deep belief nets [CITATION_1] was published by Hinton in 2006, the neural network research has been re-activated, which opened a new era of deep neural network. Deep learning has gradually achieved breakthrough in image recognition [CITATION_2] , voice recognition [CITATION_3] , text Processing [CITATION_4] and other areas.",
  "correct_citation": {
